title: Andrew Sheets: Can Central Banks Keep Up with Market Expectations?
description: On today’s podcast, Chief Cross Asset Strategist Andrew Sheets looks at how the expectations markets are placing on central banks, as much as the actions of the banks themselves, are affecting outcomes.
